    "description": "Angkor 5: Volcano's Verge is a thrilling Match-3 game that takes you on an unforgettable journey to a mystical island where the legendary temple of Angkor Wat is under construction. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs the construction on the temple intensifies, the ancient volcano beneath the island unexpectedly stirs, threatening to erupt and engulf the island. It's up to you to match the enchanted gems, solve brain-teasing puzzles, and uncover hidden secrets to break the curse and save Angkor Wat.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nProgress through 100 unique match-3 levels, master diverse minigames and help the people of Angkor construct their magnificent temple, stone by magical stone.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAre your gem matching skills up to the task?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✪ Engaging Storyline<br />\r\n✪ Unique Match 3 gameplay<br />\r\n✪ Jigsaw, Slider, Solitaire, and Memory minigames<br />\r\n✪ 100 levels of fun match making<br />\r\n✪ Customizable gameplay options<br />\r\n✪ Beautiful artwork reminiscent of the great Angkor Wat",
